data.description: Under contract-accepting backup offers. SELLER MOTIVATED! Welcome to this remarkable single-family residence that offers the perfect blend of comfort and luxury. Located in the picturesque community of Davenport, this exquisite property boasts an array of features that make it an ideal family home. With four spacious bedrooms, this home provides ample space for the entire family. The master bedroom is situated upstairs, offering privacy and a peaceful retreat. Enjoy the convenience of three full baths, ensuring that busy mornings run smoothly and everyone can enjoy their own space.  The open-concept kitchen is a culinary enthusiast's dream. It features stone counters, a range, dishwasher, disposal, microwave, and refrigerator. The eating space in the kitchen makes family meals and entertaining a breeze. The high ceilings and open floorplan create a sense of spaciousness and airiness, making it perfect for both everyday living and entertaining guests. Walk-in closets provide ample storage space for all your belongings, helping you stay organized and clutter-free. The community offers a playground, providing the perfect space for outdoor fun and play with friends. On sunny days, take a refreshing dip in the community pool, a great place to cool off and relax with neighbors and friends. This property at 339 Buchannan Dr., Davenport, FL 33837, is not just a house; it's a home where you can build lasting memories. With a beautiful interior and fantastic community amenities, it's the perfect place to live life to the fullest. Seller is motivated to make this your new home, so don't miss the opportunity to make this house your new home! And for those with furry family members, there's a community dog park for them to enjoy as well.
